165
00:09:13,986 --> 00:09:15,858
Sì, bello.

166
00:09:17,902 --> 00:09:19,224
Così.

167
00:09:22,082 --> 00:09:22,737
Oh, mio Dio.

168
00:09:22,788 --> 00:09:24,464
